name: Connect The Dots T-shirt
description:
The cute little package contains a hand printed connect-the-dots T-shirt, a non-permanent marker and instructions. The monus maan* felt markers contain special ink that is washable at 40 degrees and is suitable for small children. Step 1: Connect-the-dots with the special marker Step 2: Wear with proud Step 3: Wash Step 4: Start all over again! The monus maan* connect-the-dots T-shirt were featured on the Dutch Design Week 2010.

name: Poster - please consider ...
description:
Extra large silkscreen print 'Please consider the environment before printing this e-mail' by monus maan*. Limited Edition of 3.

You've seen the message on a thousand emails. A good initiative, but over the years the data transfer for this message is probably worse for the environment than the few prints.

We believe that you should always consider the environment, not only when printing. 

Size: 65 x 100 cm.

name: Pop Rocks original cherry
description:
Cherry Pop Rocks Crackling Candy is still popping after 30 years! This Limited Edition Cherry Pop Rocks package pays homage to the iconic brand as it features Retro "Anniversary" packaging and the original cherry flavor! 

Pop Rocks Original Cherry comes in 9.5 gram packs (0.33 oz.).

name: Good & Plenty
description:
Oh la la! Good & plenty candy; a capsule shaped cylinder of sweet licorice coated in a hard candy shell. 

Good & plenty was first produced in 1893 and is the oldest branded candy in the United States. 

Good & plenty comes in boxes of 51 grams (1.8 OZ.).

name: Big Cherry® Bar
description:
Each Big Cherry® Bar is individually-wrapped and contains a real maraschino cherry at the center, mixed with bright pink goo. As a cherry on top; it's layered with chocolate and peanut hunks! 

Golf ball-sized, Big Cherry® Bars are a delicious three-biter. Yum yum!

Important: note that Big Cherries are higher than 3 centimeters. Therefor we need to ship them as a package. Depending on the other items you buy this could increase your shipping costs.

Each Big Cherry® is approx. 50 gram (1.75 oz.).

name: Charms Blow Pops Cherry
description:
Charms Cherry Blow Pops are a classic lollipop favorite with a mouthwatering sweet cherry flavor! 

These are a delicious treat with bubble gum under the hard candy shell, making the candy last even when the pop is gone! 

Have a break, have a Blow Pop.

name: Wonka Chocolate Bars
description:
No you are not dreaming. This is real Wonka chocolate. I repeat: REAL WONKA CHOCOLATE. 

Wonka bars contain magical milk chocolate bursting with little bits of crunchy graham cracker. They weight about 75 grams (2.6 oz.). 

Fresh from the Willy Wonka Candy Factory! Get it while it's hot!

name: Pop Rocks Cotton Candy
description:
The latest Limited Edition Pop Rock that creates a cotton candy  explosion in your mouth. Pop! Pop! Pop!

Comes in fancy-shmancy 9.5 gram packs (0.33 oz.).

name: Pop Rocks Bubble Gum
description:
Get a load of this; Pop Rocks - the mouth popping candy - now changes into bubble gum! Whoohaa! The best of both worlds! 

Pop Rocks Bubble Gum comes in 9.5 gram packs (0.33 oz.). Too cool for school.

name: Wonka Tinglerz
description:
Another amazing invention from the wacky Willy Wonka factory! Imagine Pop Rocks combined with rice in a soft, tasty chocolate shell. Then you'll have Wonka Tinglerz. A sweet, smooth poppin' chocolate candy. Or as they say in spanish: Chocolattos que revientan en tu boca!

Both delicious & a whole lot of fun; everything candy should be!

Wonka Tinglerz come in bags of 28.3 gram (1 OZ.).

name: Garbage Pail Kids Series #5
description:
Garbage Pail Kids originally released between 1985 & 1988 were immensely popular at the time. GPK stickers or cards often came with a hard, tasteless chewing gum. 

They were published in many countries, but also banned in many schools.

These #5 series cards are a very hard-to-get 2006 re-releases of the original 1986 series. 

A package contains 6 stickers and comes without a gum.

name: Charms Cotton Candy Pops
description:
Forget Chupa Chups. With these unique Charms 'Fluffy Stuff' Cotton Candy Pops the sweet flavors of cotton candy are packed into each of these yummy lollipops. 

Fresh from the Carnival!

name: Pop Rocks Topping
description:
A full can of chocolate covered Pop Rocks candy.. The perfect topping for pancakes, ice cream, cupcakes, yogurt or fruit!

Pop Rocks Topping comes in a 115 gram can (4.06 oz.). 
Best before: 05 2013

name: Long Boys Chocolate
description: Traditional old fashioned southern treats. Chocolate long boys are chewy caramels blended with real chocolate!

name: Wonka NERDS® double dip
description:
Double dipped Lemonade/wild cherry and apple/watermelon NERDS® from Wonka - Tiny, tangy, crunchy candy pieces of candy!

Straight from the Wonka factory: a fresh box of delicious double dipped Wonka's NERDS®! One of the most popular Wonka products on the market, with a powerfully tangy taste!

Fresh lemonade-coated wild cherry is in one side of the box, and the crazy combination of apple-coated watermelon is in the other side. Eat seperate, or mix 'm up!

name: Pop Rocks Cola
description:
For years rumors persist that eating Pop Rocks and drinking cola will cause a person's stomach to explode. Well, from now on all you Coke & Pop rock fans don't have to worry about that anymore! Pop Rocks Cola combines your favourite drink with the best popping candy!

Pop Rocks Cola comes in 7 gram packs (0.245 oz.).

name: Hershey's Whatchamacallit
description:
This peanut flavoured crisp candy topped with a layer of caramel and dipped in chocolate has a name and a taste that's hard to forget! 

If you ask us, you may also call it delicious. Don't leave without it.

Each Whatchamacallit is 45 gram (1.6 oz.).

name: Pop Rocks Dips Strawberry
description:
What a combination; pop rocks and lollipops! 

Grab some of the popping sensation that is sweeping the nation, strawberry flavoured popping candy with lollipop. And if this isn't enough; these packages include a fancy schmancy tattoo!

Pop Rocks Dips Strawberry comes in 18 gram packs (0.63 oz.).

name: Wonka NERDS®
description:
Grape and Strawberry Wonka NERDS® - Tiny, crunchy candy pieces of candy.

One of the most popular Wonka products on the market, with a powerfully tangy taste! Fruity grape candy is in one side of the box, intense sweet strawberry in the other. Eat seperate, or mix 'm up!

Wonka NERDS® come in a 50g box.

name: Dr Dryels Halstabletter
description:
This classic from Swedish candy brand Malaco has a split personality. Dr. Dryels are very fresh cough drops, but you can also DRINK them when you have a sore throught! 

Just drop 8 or 10 Dryels in a glass boiling milk or tea. Stir it a little and drink it as hot as possible. You'll soon start to sound as Susan Boyle again!

Dr Dryels Halstabletter come in nice retro looking 75 gram bags.
